WHY YOU ARE SEEING THIS ERROR
'ngrok' is not recognized...

👉 Means:

ngrok is not installed, OR

Installed but not added to PATH

🚀 ✅ SIMPLE FIX (STEP BY STEP)
🔧 STEP 1: Download ngrok

Go here:
👉 https://ngrok.com/download

Choose:
👉 Windows (64-bit)

🔧 STEP 2: Extract ZIP

You’ll get:

ngrok.exe

👉 Extract it to any folder
Example:

C:\ngrok\
🔧 STEP 3: Run from that folder

Open Command Prompt in that folder:

cd C:\ngrok

Then run:

ngrok http 3000
✅ DONE 🎉

You will see:

Forwarding https://xxxx.ngrok.io -> http://localhost:3000

👉 Share this link with your team

